h a level of difficulty that will mean that many of us will not be able to play.</P><P><BR><center>The 3yr old level 51 Necro...<img src=icon_smile_clown.gif border=0 align=middle><BR>The caster balancing is going really well for us Necromancers.<BR><font color=blue>Think about the word THONG.</font id=blue><BR></center><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
